'''胆酸'''（{{lang-en|Cholic acid}}，也被称为'''3α,7α,12α-三羟基-5β-胆烷-24-羧酸'''，3α,7α,12α-trihydroxy-5β-cholan-24-oic acid）是[[胆汁酸|胆汁酸]]的主要成分<ref name="isbn0-7817-9340-8">{{cite book |author=Colleen Smith |author2=Lieberman, Michael |author3=Marks, Dawn B. |author4=Allan D. Marks |title=Marks' essential medical biochemistry |url=https://archive.org/details/marksessentialme0000lieb |publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins |location=Hagerstwon, MD |year=2007 |pages= |isbn=978-0-7817-9340-7 |oclc= |doi= |accessdate=}}</ref>，不溶于水，可溶于[[乙醇|乙醇]]和[[乙酸|乙酸]]，固态为白色晶体，其盐类被称为'''胆酸盐'''（{{lang-en|cholates}}）。

胆酸和[[鹅去氧胆酸|鹅去氧胆酸]]是[[胆汁酸|胆汁酸]]的两大主要成分，由[[肝脏|肝脏]]代谢[[胆固醇|胆固醇]]生成，这两种主要胆汁酸在人体内的浓度大致相等<ref name="pmid1244533">{{cite journal |vauthors=Bennion LJ, Ginsberg RL, Gernick MB, Bennett PH |title=Effects of oral contraceptives on the gallbladder bile of normal women |journal=N. Engl. J. Med. |volume=294 |issue=4 |pages=189–92 | date=January 1976 |pmid=1244533 |doi=10.1056/NEJM197601222940403 |url=}}</ref>。胆酸的衍生物主要由胆酸-辅酶A（cholyl-CoA）生成，其中[[辅酶A|CoA]]可以与[[甘氨酸|甘氨酸]]或[[牛磺酸|牛磺酸]]交换，生成[[甘氨胆酸|甘氨胆酸]]或[[牛磺胆酸|牛磺胆酸]]<ref name="pmid19346330">{{cite journal |author=Chiang JY |title=Bile acids: regulation of synthesis |journal=Journal of Lipid Research |volume=50 |issue=10 |pages=1955–66 |date=October 2009 |pmid=19346330 |pmc=2739756 |doi=10.1194/jlr.R900010-JLR200 |url=http://www.jlr.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=19346330 |access-date=2019-06-14 |archive-date=2019-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191218105652/http://www.jlr.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=19346330 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

